Hey all, using post from above this is how I got all to work:

Win7 Pro 64 bit
CS5.5 Master collection

Install the suite with a serial provided by the keygen by rolling back your system clock to June 2011.

Once this is finished, run the patch to block activate.adobe.com in your host file.

For extra precaution, you can block all access to *.adobe.com with your firewall.

Then download the 2 files from here to replace the dll files in the adobe folder:


By using the windows search function, find all files named atmlib.dll and replace them with the downloaded ones above. Ne sure to copy the correct version (i.e. 64 and 32 bit).

Enjoy!!
